679
00:29:59,626 --> 00:30:03,216
Size Classes is a feature of iOS
8 and Xcode 6 that allows you


680
00:30:03,216 --> 00:30:05,746
to specify how your View
Controller and your UI adapt


681
00:30:05,746 --> 00:30:07,976
